// The lobby menu is now server-authoritative. Pressing Enter in the lobby sends "openmenu" to the
// server (see game.nvgt), which builds and pushes the menu; the client renders it via show_server_menu
// (menu_parser.nvgt) and replies "menuresult". The old client-rendered lobby_menu() / join_room_menu()
// were removed; the server handles create/join in menu.nvgt + net.nvgt.
